        public NOTES_COLOR getColor()
        If the BARREC_HAS_COLOR bit is set in the Flags field then immediately following this structure there will be a WORD that identifies the value of the color. This color value comes from the defines in the file COLORID.H that begin with NOTES_COLOR_xxx
